  visualOnlyNeverGameplayAuthority: 1
  notes: Player-facing terrain dressing uses real Unity prefab assemblies and Terrain
    Sample Asset Pack ground replacements when installed. The Stage16 map is dressed
    as two vertically stacked 32-cell battlefield sections with classic military
    RTS-style cliffs, boulders, outpost pads, wreckage, and route details. Reference
    sheets are art direction only and must not be used as runtime terrain cards.
